high_descs: Turn and go to the sink behind you.
Pick up the egg closer to the back of the sink.
Go to your right to the stove.
Put the egg into the microwave above the stove.
Return to the sink.
Pick up the egg that is in the sink.
Turn right and go back to the stove.
Put the egg beside the other egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Move two eggs from the sink to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and take a small step to your left then walk to the sink.
Pick up the egg that's above another egg.
Turn right and walk to the stove then take a small step right.
Put the egg in the microwave that's above the stove.
Walk back to where you got the first egg.
Pick up the egg that's still in the sink.
Walk back to the microwave.
Put this egg in the microwave too then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put two eggs in the microwave.
